Translation</b>，感兴趣的读者可以在<a href="http://www.amazon.com/Chinglish-Oliver-Lutz-Radtke/dp/1423603354/ref=pd_bbs_sr_1/102-3585860-7148153?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;amp;qid=1184492235&amp;sr=8-1">Amazon</a>购买。
